{
  "stem": "9701.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And by 1942, I think, or 1943, another girl and I decided we were going to branch out and we're going to go and work someplace else.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we both worked for Harrods department store in London.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were making children's dresses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was the same department that made the clothes for now Queen Elizabeth and her sister Margaret, but we didn't get to make those clothes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I think in late 1943 I decided that I really needed to do something for the war effort.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I worked-- changed jobs and worked in a war factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I worked in a couple of war factories until the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- also, while I lived in this girls' home, there were-- again, you know, I mentioned in the beginning that I felt different.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I felt different there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In my spare time, I attended a college and I took courses in literature and psychology, not towards a degree, but just to-- for my own edification.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And a lot of the girls in this home were interested in I guess finding a husband.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the American army was there, so they went to the dances to meet GIs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Some of the girls became-- I guess, because they probably came from very good homes, but they were so desperate for love some of them actually became prostitutes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "One of them encouraged me to join her, but I resisted that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was a lot of stealing going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And some of it was really not to get maybe something of value, because I remember one of my roommates had photographs of her parents stolen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was, you know, I think, someone searching for love.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Maybe she didn't have pictures of her parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was suicide.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
